  "original_title": "\u0b89\u0ba3\u0bb5\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1 \u0bae\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bc6\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bca\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f \u0b86\u0bb8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc7\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0baf \u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc6\u0b9f\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bc0\u0bb0\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Australian cricketers go to restaurant and get electrocuted",
      "body_lines": [
        "Australian cricketer Butt Cummins has been hit by a power outage in Sri Lanka while visiting a local restaurant.",
        "He also posted a post on his Twitter page.",
        "\"Earlier this week we went to a restaurant where there was a power outage. We are waiting for the power to come on and dinner will continue as soon as the power comes on.\"",
        "\"Sri Lanka is going through a difficult time now, but people have surprised us and we are grateful to be here,\" he added on his Twitter page."
      ],
